All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
App
The App class serves as the entry point for the application.
Applicant
Represents an applicant in the system.
ApplicantController
Controller class for managing applicant-related operations, such as viewing projects, submitting applications, and handling enquiries.
ApplicantDao
Data Access Object (DAO) interface for managing applicant-related operations.
ApplicantView
View class for managing applicant-related interactions with the system.
Application
Represents an application submitted by an applicant for a housing project.
ApplicationCSVDao
Implementation of the ApplicationDao interface for managing applications using a CSV file as the data source.
ApplicationDao
Data Access Object (DAO) interface for managing application-related operations.
ApplicationStatus
Enum representing the status of an application.
AuthController
Controller class for handling authentication-related operations.
Enquiry
Represents an enquiry submitted by an applicant for a specific project.
EnquiryCSVDao
Implementation of the EnquiryDao interface for managing enquiries using a CSV file as the data source.
EnquiryDao
Data Access Object (DAO) interface for managing enquiry-related operations.
InitController
Controller class for initializing the application by reading data from CSV files.
LoginView
View class for managing the login process in the BTO Application System.
Manager
Represents a manager in the system.
ManagerController
Controller class for managing operations related to managers, such as creating, editing, and deleting projects, handling officer registrations, managing applications, and responding to enquiries.
ManagerView
The ManagerView class provides the user interface for managers to interact with the system.
Officer
Represents an officer in the system.
OfficerController
Controller class for managing officer-related operations, such as project registration, application management, and enquiry handling.
OfficerController.RegistrationStatus
Represents the registration status of an officer for a project.
OfficerView
The OfficerView class provides the user interface for officers to interact with the system.
Project
Represents a housing project in the system.
Project.FlatTypeDetails
Represents the details of a flat type in the project.
ProjectCSVDao
Implementation of the ProjectDao interface for managing projects using a CSV file as the data source.
ProjectDao
Data Access Object (DAO) interface for managing project-related operations.
User
Represents a user in the system.
UserCSVDao
Implementation of the UserDao interface for managing user data using CSV files.
UserDao
Data Access Object (DAO) interface for managing user-related operations.
UserView
The UserView class serves as a base class for user-related views.
